{"word":"Usury","slug":"usury","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Usury</b> Interest, not necessarily unreasonable exaction, but all income from loans.<br/> Forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=25'>Exo 22:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=37'>Lev 25:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=19'>Deu 23:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=15&verse=5'>Psa 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=28&verse=8'>Pro 28:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=15&verse=10'>Jer 15:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=18&verse=8'>Eze 18:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=18&verse=13'>Eze 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=18&verse=17'>Eze 18:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=12'>Eze 22:12</a><br/> Exaction of, rebuked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=5&verse=13'>Neh 5:13</a><br/> Authorized, of strangers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=20'>Deu 23:20</a><br/> Exacted by Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=12'>Eze 22:12</a><br/> Just men innocent of the vice of requiring<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=18&verse=8'>Eze 18:8</a><br/><a href='S:Interest'>Interest</a>; <a href='S:Money'>Money</a>"}]}